txt.en: 'The stable is important, but there is much to do to bring it to usefulness. Horses do not feed and wash and take care of themselves; there are many pieces of equipment needed to properly take care of them. The more of these we get into place, the better a stable we will have, and the better our horses will be.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
